{"tid":1275433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-01T19:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T11:06:35.000Z","uid":62043,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2bc6b072f6df4d1f281e30e934b32dd44359a0d8","tid":1275433,"uid":62043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:52:48.000Z","msg":"發夢琴晚留守到啱啱先翻<br />\n朝早龍匯俾人趕同夜晚守龍和都係前排<br />\n我覺得琴晚開會有兩個人講得好啱<br />\n「上得前線就要有覺悟，預咗食煙俾人打」<br />\n「真心我冇覺悟，好多人都一樣，冇人會怪你，但請你唔好上前線」<br />\n好簡單就講出點解每次都守唔到，一見有狗衝前線已經唔見咗一半，係冇撚得守<br />\n唔係話要分化，但冇心理準備個啲可唔可以去後面做哨兵又好運物資又好，唔好每一次都俾人衝散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8230a62a37d7484ad842c341236173a0eb5f48b8","tid":1275433,"uid":62043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:55:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa28eb82059cafdac83e2d3897786d2ff6d90c93","tid":1275433,"uid":62043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:58:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55b4dafac2001f35d6486e00bb293a0077ae83cc","tid":1275433,"uid":60578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:01:37.000Z","msg":"呢個真 一個走 就引到後面驚果d又走<br />\n之後真前線果班見冇人又退"},{"pid":"6ac02badc515a0b8d5b665adf9092e4626170ee6","tid":1275433,"uid":62043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:04:38.000Z","msg":"要贏真係要好好分工，唔啱自己唔好勉強"},{"pid":"898bd09ebd30716339afd7db39aad704c85cbe0c","tid":1275433,"uid":269285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:06:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35cf0e128f259b29a70a53c96b36af237eecb8fb","tid":1275433,"uid":62043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:09:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb16f22628144edc806945477ee3e6b4d8f5efe3","tid":1275433,"uid":62043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:14:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f282839b550eb3a38e6429bc19c0ca39756c934a","tid":1275433,"uid":62043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:21:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eba6e75287261914b8aee1179d0a3b226fe630cc","tid":1275433,"uid":62043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:41:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"163266d942fe0f4db3b56c2cfa6bd45ad33e9993","tid":1275433,"uid":150930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:45:00.000Z","msg":"岩 前線見後面冇人實好灰<br />\n但入夜好多人走都係事實<br />\n夜晚重適唔適合守都要好好考慮<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"b2a498fbd9f97c7b293f1ff401009b7467a27b13","tid":1275433,"uid":50762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T20:46:55.000Z","msg":"唔好怪佢地<br />\n最尾夜晚守立法會 其實龍和拖左十分鐘幫到好多<br />\n我見好多人都明顯無咩經驗 係死頂架咋<br />\n<br />\n其實好多時係無人上 啲人逼住上前線<br />\n真係有覺悟既前線 未必夠散佈係各條線度"},{"pid":"825f7f76f71fa5575f58a1b6552fd66674fc22a3","tid":1275433,"uid":62043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T23:42:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd50ba8f7bd9143f7acbf45aa9effd864d73aba8","tid":1275433,"uid":62043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:14:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e35b3b1dd5b5cb0e44c13be0caca776745f28379","tid":1275433,"uid":4875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:17:38.000Z","msg":"你有無上過前線架，龍和一黎黑旗，前線已經硬食gas幾粒都唔肯走住，最後真係白到睇唔到先退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申發夢夢境"},{"pid":"df749ef7e1439001a4a1043b0a51a5f839b3ce78","tid":1275433,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68540d4ee17a42c752e9d1e18b1be99bfb0cc950","tid":1275433,"uid":62043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e35b3b1dd5b5cb0e44c13be0caca776745f28379","tid":1275433,"uid":4875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:17:38.000Z","msg":"你有無上過前線架，龍和一黎黑旗，前線已經硬食gas幾粒都唔肯走住，最後真係白到睇唔到先退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申發夢夢境"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:27:43.000Z","msg":"第一粒已經走咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9273282a04af4402ed4aa622af8e001af4daa7b6","tid":1275433,"uid":4875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68540d4ee17a42c752e9d1e18b1be99bfb0cc950","tid":1275433,"uid":62043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e35b3b1dd5b5cb0e44c13be0caca776745f28379","tid":1275433,"uid":4875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:17:38.000Z","msg":"你有無上過前線架，龍和一黎黑旗，前線已經硬食gas幾粒都唔肯走住，最後真係白到睇唔到先退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申發夢夢境"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:27:43.000Z","msg":"第一粒已經走咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:06:35.000Z","msg":"發夢我就第一排，唔知你地後邊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}